<b>Titlepage</b> for <i>Typographische Gestaltung</i> written and designed by Jan Tschichold using <a href="/wiki/City_(typeface)" title="City (typeface)">City Medium</a> and <a href="/wiki/Bodoni" title="Bodoni">Bodoni</a>. Published in 1932 by the Benno Schwabe &amp; Co. publishing house.</div>
</div>
