<p><b>Jan Tschichold</b> (<span class="mw-formatted-date" title="1902-04-02"><a href="/wiki/April_2" title="April 2">2 April</a> <a href="/wiki/1902" title="1902">1902</a></span> <a href="/wiki/Leipzig" title="Leipzig">Leipzig</a>, <a href="/wiki/Germany" title="Germany">Germany</a> â€“ <span class="mw-formatted-date" title="1974-08-11"><a href="/wiki/August_11" title="August 11">11 August</a> <a href="/wiki/1974" title="1974">1974</a></span> <a href="/wiki/Locarno" title="Locarno">Locarno</a>, <a href="/wiki/Switzerland" title="Switzerland">Switzerland</a>) was a <a href="/wiki/Typography" title="Typography">typographer</a>, book designer, teacher and writer.</p>
